  "title": "Senior/ Clinic Executive (Healthcare) Ref: GDC",
  "description": "<p><strong># Salary Up to $5800 + Excellent Benefits</strong></p><p><strong># Work Location (Northeast)</strong></p><p><strong># Commit to 5.5 days work week (Half Day Saturdays)</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Our client, a leading healthcare organisation in Singapore is currently seeking a candidate to join them as a Senior Clinic Executive/ Assistant Clinic Operations Manager.</strong></p><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Oversee the smooth functioning and operation of the clinics</li><li>Oversees clinic appointments, overall staff deployment and resource allocation</li><li>Ensures guidelines and procedures related to clinic services are adhered to by all relevant personnel</li><li>Handles Public Relation cases at first line and assist clinic staff in dealing with difficult situations</li><li>Maintain discipline in compliance with policies</li><li>Ensures timely submission of monthly reports and accuracy of clinical indicators</li></ul><p><br /></p><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Minimum Degree in any discipline</li><li>Minimum 1-2 years of relevant experience in clinic or healthcare setting</li><li>Commit to a 5.5 Day work week, inclusive of Saturday work (Half-Day)</li></ul><p></p><p>Interested and qualified applicants, please email your resume in MS Word format to <strong>denise.tan@celecti.com.sg.</strong></p><p>Denise Charlene Tan Su-yen (Ms.) |\nCEI Reg. No.: R1104480 | EA Licence No. 16C8045 | Tel no.: 9669 2031</p>",
